    <div class="row" style="width:100vh; font-family:'Gill Sans MT';">
        <div class="card-body" style="background-color: rgba(247,247,247,255); margin-top:10vh; margin-left:2vh; width:100vh; color:black;">
            <ul class="nav nav-pills mb-3" id="pills-tab" role="tablist">
                <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
                    <button class="nav-link active" id="pills-home-tab" data-bs-toggle="pill" data-bs-target="#pills-home" type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="pills-home" aria-selected="true" style="background-color:rgba(247,247,247,255);color:black;">Opis</button>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
                    <button class="nav-link" id="pills-profile-tab" data-bs-toggle="pill" data-bs-target="#pills-profile" type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="pills-profile" aria-selected="false" style="background-color:rgba(247,247,247,255);color:black;">Specyfikacja techniczna</button>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
                    <button class="nav-link" id="pills-contact-tab" data-bs-toggle="pill" data-bs-target="#pills-contact" type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="pills-contact" aria-selected="false" style="background-color:rgba(247,247,247,255);color:black;">Aktywacja kodu</button>
                </li>
            </ul>
            <div class="tab-content" id="pills-tabContent" style="background-color: rgba(247,247,247,255);">
                <div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="pills-home" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="pills-home-tab">Czternastą odsłoną serii Battlefield będzie Battlefield 1 i będzie kontynuował sukcesy swoich poprzedników. Tym razem popularna gra FPS zostanie osadzona w I wojnie światowej, pierwszej tego typu grze Battlefield.
                    @Model.Opis
                </div>
                <div class="tab-pane fade" id="pills-profile" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="pills-profile-tab">...</div>
                <div class="tab-pane fade" id="pills-contact" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="pills-contact-tab">...</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
